text: SÄ“misi Kioa Lafu Sika (born 31 January 1968) is a Tongan politician. He is a member of the Tongan Parliament. Sika was the acting Prime Minister of Tonga from 12 September 2019 through 27 September 2019. He is a member of the Democratic Party of the Friendly Islands. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Tonga
